  {{#demo.example name="threes-pane.hbs"}}

  {{#uxs-window}}
    {{#uxs-pane index=true style=indexStyle padded=padded}}
      {{uxs-heading "Index"}}
      {{#uxs-list bordered=true as |list|}}
        {{#list.item as |item|}}
          {{item.title "Item One"}}
        {{/list.item}}
        {{#list.item as |item|}}
          {{item.title "Item Two"}}
        {{/list.item}}
        {{#list.item as |item|}}
          {{item.title "Item Three"}}
        {{/list.item}}
      {{/uxs-list}}
    {{/uxs-pane}}
    {{#uxs-pane detail=true style=detailStyle padded=padded}}
      {{uxs-heading "Detail"}}
      {{#uxs-content}}
      Turpis in eros morbi scelerisque nisl condimentum ut ultricies scelerisque sociosqu venenatis cum parturient id eleifend sodales vitae rutrum sociosqu accumsan.
      {{/uxs-content}}
